Package maltcms.commands.fragments2d.peakfinding

Interface Summary
IBidirectionalBestHit Interface for an BBH algorithm used by SeededRegionGrowing.
IPeakExporter Provides some methods to export relevant peak information.
IPeakIdentification Supports a method to identify a peak.
IPeakIntegration Provides some methods to do a peak integration.
 

Class Summary
BidirectionalBestHit Will compute a list of bidirectional best hits.
FastBidirectionalBestHit Will compute a list of bidirectional best hits.
PeakExporter Implementation of an peak exporter.
PeakIdentification Will do the identification.
PeakIntegration Does the Peak Integration on basis of the unique masses.
SeededRegionGrowing Will do the snakefail.
